title: Rx pills found near Jim Carrey's ex-gal-pal's death spot
text:
*Washington D.C., Oct 4 (ANI): As a part of latest investigation, cops have found three bottles of Rx pills beside Jim Carrey's former gal-pal Cathriona White's bed, who committed suicide by overdosing on drugs.*
Washington D.C., Oct 4 (ANI): As a part of latest investigation, cops have found three bottles of Rx pills beside Jim Carrey's former gal-pal Cathriona White's bed, who committed suicide by overdosing on drugs. In addition to this, the pills, which included Ambien (sleep aid), Percocet (painkiller) and Propranolol (blood pressure/heart), were all prescribed by a fictitious male, who is reportedly the 'Dumb and Dumber' star's alias, TMZ.com reported. A source informed that there must be a reason to believe White may have taken the pills from the 53-year-old actor's house, but the reason hasn't been confirmed. (ANI) Â»
